            <h1>Health and care</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/helse_og_omsorg_150x113.jpg" alt="Healthcare personel holding a patients' hand" /></div>
            <p class="textIngress">The Government endeavours to ensure that everyone, irrespective of their personal finances and where they live, has access to good health and care services of equal standard.</p>
            <img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/helse_og_omsorg_150x113.jpg" alt="Healthcare personel holding a patients' hand" class="temaIngressImg" />
            <div class="descriptionText"><p><em>The Ministry of Health and Care Services</em> has chief responsibility for health policy, public health, health services, municipal services for the elderly and disabled, health legislation and parts of social legislation in Norway.</p>
<p>On this page you will find general information and documents relating to health and care services. You can explore this topic in more detail by using the menu on the right.</p></div>
