                        Norwegian candidate for Chair of GAVI Alliance Board
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 13.08.2010]</p>
                <p>The Norwegian Government has nominated Dagfinn Høybråten (Member of the Storting and Leader of the Christian Democratic Party) as candidate for Chair of the Board of the GAVI Alliance.  </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
