                        Second Norwegian Cancer Symposium 2009
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">Speech, December 2nd 2009</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Health and Care Services, 03.12.2009]</p>
                <p>Opening speech by Minister of Health and Care Services Anne-Grete Strøm-Erichsen at the Second Norwegian Cancer Symposium 2009.</p>
                
                
