            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/hod/press-center/pressemeldinger/2009/russia-takes-over-the-chairmanship-of-th.html?id=587097" title="">
                        Russia takes over the chairmanship of the health collaboration under the Northern Dimension
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Health and Care Services, 25.11.2009]</p>
                <p>November 25 Norway hosted the Northern Dimension Partnership in Public Health and Social Well-being’s Annual Conference. At the conference, Russia formally took over the chairmanship of the Partnership from Norway. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
