            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/smk/press-center/Press-releases/2009/billions-to-improve-health-services-for-.html?id=578106" title="">
                        Billions to improve health services for women and children in developing countries
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, The Office of the Prime Minister, 24.09.2009]</p>
                <p>At a meeting at the UN in New York on 23 September, rich and poor countries pledged a total of USD 5.3 billion to improve the health of mothers and children in the world’s 49 poorest countries.  </p>
                
                
